WEBVTT

01:30.930 --> 01:34.970
[Dream of Golden Years]

01:41.509 --> 01:43.000
I once thought my life

01:43.560 --> 01:45.509
would always be bright and radiant,

01:45.509 --> 01:46.840
smooth and effortless.

01:48.590 --> 01:49.150
But then,

01:49.590 --> 01:51.120
at some unexpected turn,

01:51.200 --> 01:53.000
fate nudged the clock off course

01:53.280 --> 01:54.740
and changed my direction.

01:56.150 --> 01:57.430
The world is fickle,

01:58.120 --> 01:59.850
and losing control is the norm.

02:00.760 --> 02:03.150
From that moment on, my world

02:03.760 --> 02:05.090
became dim and chaotic.

02:07.690 --> 02:09.490
If everything could start over,

02:09.520 --> 02:11.580
would I be able to have a perfect life?

02:12.280 --> 02:13.080
Don't forget—

02:13.240 --> 02:14.240
every gift from fate

02:14.240 --> 02:15.500
comes with a price tag.

02:15.910 --> 02:16.560
And are you truly sure

02:16.560 --> 02:17.820
you want to start over?

02:18.570 --> 02:21.860
[Episode 1]
[Do you really want to start over?]

02:24.910 --> 02:28.210
[New Year, 2026]

03:37.520 --> 03:38.079
Xiaolan.

03:39.840 --> 03:40.520
Xiaolan.

03:46.160 --> 03:47.650
Wake up, Xiaolan.

03:52.870 --> 03:53.670
You're awake.

03:56.480 --> 03:57.190
Who are you?

03:59.750 --> 04:00.960
I'm your mother.

04:01.800 --> 04:02.960
Psychopath.

04:04.030 --> 04:04.750
Xiaolan.

04:06.120 --> 04:07.360
Don't scare me.

04:07.870 --> 04:08.680
Are you okay?

04:09.280 --> 04:10.080
Don't move around.

04:10.080 --> 04:11.740
Your wound hasn't healed yet.

04:12.280 --> 04:13.680
Don't touch that wound.

04:13.800 --> 04:14.530
Xia Xiaolan!

04:15.240 --> 04:17.560
Why don't you just die?

04:18.310 --> 04:18.950
Xiaolan?

04:25.310 --> 04:26.040
Xiaolan.

04:35.090 --> 04:36.620
What the hell is this place?

04:40.870 --> 04:41.400
Mr. Wang.

04:42.159 --> 04:44.290
Look at the contract you signed off on!

04:44.600 --> 04:45.330
Xia Xiaolan.

04:45.560 --> 04:47.240
How dare you talk about promotion?

04:47.240 --> 04:48.180
Because of you,

04:48.240 --> 04:50.640
our company has to pay
a huge compensation!

04:51.360 --> 04:51.800
What?

04:51.870 --> 04:52.330
Come on.

04:52.600 --> 04:54.070
Take a look at the contract yourself.

04:54.070 --> 04:56.190
See what the joint-liability clause says!

04:56.190 --> 04:57.830
It was you who signed this contract,
wasn't it?

04:57.830 --> 04:59.230
All our company's losses

04:59.430 --> 05:00.890
will be borne by you alone!

05:00.920 --> 05:01.970
You can leave now

05:02.000 --> 05:03.040
and wait to be sued!

05:03.040 --> 05:04.040
Mr. Wang, I didn't...

05:04.040 --> 05:04.630
Get lost!

05:05.680 --> 05:06.240
Mr. Wang...

05:06.240 --> 05:06.770
Get lost!

05:07.240 --> 05:08.430
If you can't pay the compensation,

05:08.430 --> 05:09.690
get ready to go to jail!

05:31.310 --> 05:33.270
Get up. Stop pretending.

05:33.480 --> 05:34.040
Xiaolan.

05:35.360 --> 05:35.890
Xiaolan?

05:36.159 --> 05:36.690
Be quiet.

05:40.510 --> 05:42.510
Our Ziyu is a college student.

05:42.600 --> 05:44.920
She's going to move to the city
in the future.

05:44.920 --> 05:46.560
How could Jianhua possibly
take a liking to you?

05:46.560 --> 05:47.270
She got in!

05:48.190 --> 05:49.310
Yeah, she got in. She got in.

05:49.310 --> 05:51.390
What kind of sin
has our Xia family committed

05:51.390 --> 05:53.040
to end up getting
a daughter-in-law like you?

05:53.040 --> 05:54.070
Giving birth to a daughter

05:54.070 --> 05:55.750
who has no shame, either!

05:57.270 --> 05:57.870
Get out of my way!

05:57.870 --> 05:58.480
What are you doing?

05:58.480 --> 05:59.310
Move aside!

05:59.600 --> 06:00.160
I'll beat her to death!

06:00.160 --> 06:00.960
Xia, don't...

06:06.970 --> 06:07.930
Xiaolan!

06:07.960 --> 06:09.630
This has nothing to do with us.

06:10.240 --> 06:11.840
She crashed into it herself.

06:12.560 --> 06:13.040
Xiaolan!

06:13.040 --> 06:14.480
This has nothing to do with us.

06:14.480 --> 06:15.590
She crashed into it herself.

06:15.590 --> 06:17.160
She's just pretending, you know?

06:17.160 --> 06:18.040
She's just faking it.

06:18.040 --> 06:19.750
Quite convincing, huh?

06:23.270 --> 06:25.270
Could it be that I've transmigrated

06:25.680 --> 06:28.240
and become another Xia Xiaolan?

06:29.870 --> 06:30.270
Wait.

06:30.510 --> 06:31.480
Is this for real?

06:31.920 --> 06:33.580
She's completely shameless,

06:33.680 --> 06:35.680
messing around with that scoundrel

06:36.120 --> 06:37.510
and even seducing her sister's man.

06:37.510 --> 06:38.950
Auntie, don't get angry with her.

06:38.950 --> 06:41.150
She's really going to be the death of me.

06:45.159 --> 06:45.830
Xiaolan.

06:46.190 --> 06:46.750
Xiaolan!

06:47.120 --> 06:48.430
Xiaolan, you can't get out there!

06:48.430 --> 06:49.800
I'm so mad.

06:50.560 --> 06:51.159
What's going on?

06:51.159 --> 06:52.430
Isn't that the shameless

06:52.430 --> 06:53.480
Xia Xiaolan?

06:53.980 --> 06:55.380
Why is she coming out now?

06:55.630 --> 06:57.800
I've become someone else,

06:58.680 --> 07:01.340
yet all I face are still
accusations and gossip.

07:01.360 --> 07:02.760
What kind of fate is this?

07:05.070 --> 07:07.530
I did once hope to be
the center of attention.

07:08.240 --> 07:11.120
But definitely not like this.

07:12.560 --> 07:13.720
Xia Xiaolan.

07:14.270 --> 07:15.190
You actually dare to show your face?

07:15.190 --> 07:16.650
Grandmother... And Aunt?

07:16.670 --> 07:18.190
Aren't you ashamed enough?

07:18.190 --> 07:19.000
You jinx.

07:19.080 --> 07:20.560
Didn't you say you want to die?

07:20.560 --> 07:21.760
So why don't you do it?

07:22.390 --> 07:24.390
Why don't you just go ahead and do it?

07:26.720 --> 07:27.190
You...

07:27.650 --> 07:28.430
Blocking me from hitting her, huh?

07:28.430 --> 07:29.270
Not fighting back?

07:29.270 --> 07:30.480
Mother! Mother, I'm begging you!

07:30.480 --> 07:31.190
She's even kneeling down.

07:31.190 --> 07:32.430
Please spare Xiaolan
and give her a way out.

07:32.430 --> 07:33.830
I'm begging you, Mother.

07:33.870 --> 07:34.830
Whether it's a dead end or a way out,

07:34.830 --> 07:36.030
she chose it herself.

07:36.560 --> 07:38.120
She disgraced herself!

07:38.750 --> 07:41.080
Why should I be the one
to give her a way out?

07:41.720 --> 07:42.270
Exactly!

07:42.430 --> 07:44.310
Even Hongxia has been affected by her.

07:44.310 --> 07:44.840
Hongxia!

07:45.000 --> 07:45.870
Why are you still standing there?

07:45.870 --> 07:46.620
Don't you feel embarrassed?

07:46.620 --> 07:47.820
Take the kids inside.

07:49.360 --> 07:50.020
Shameless.

07:50.720 --> 07:51.240
Look.

07:52.240 --> 07:53.070
Xia Xiaolan, look around you.

07:53.070 --> 07:53.870
Just look.

07:54.360 --> 07:56.360
Look around—every man and woman,

07:56.360 --> 07:57.390
old and young in this whole village

07:57.390 --> 07:59.159
thinks you're a disgrace!

07:59.950 --> 08:01.160
A bunch of haters.

08:01.480 --> 08:02.630
One

08:02.950 --> 08:04.610
only knows how to chase men...

08:04.950 --> 08:06.240
Mother, please stop hitting Xiaolan.

08:06.240 --> 08:06.560
I'm begging you.

08:06.560 --> 08:08.720
And the other can't even bear a son.

08:09.360 --> 08:10.830
If she had died earlier...

08:10.830 --> 08:11.920
This old hag just won't stop.

08:11.920 --> 08:13.040
It would have been doing a good deed

08:13.040 --> 08:14.870
for the Xia family, you know?

08:16.430 --> 08:17.510
You old hag.

08:17.630 --> 08:18.830
Watch your mouth.

08:18.830 --> 08:19.750
That'd be the only good deed
you can do for yourself.

08:19.750 --> 08:22.080
Mother, she actually dares to insult you!

08:22.600 --> 08:23.830
What are you all making a fuss about?

08:23.830 --> 08:25.270
Watching this family drama
is great fun, huh?

08:25.270 --> 08:26.530
Are you even involved?

08:26.800 --> 08:28.600
Do you even know what actually happened?

08:28.600 --> 08:29.870
Throwing dirt at others

08:29.870 --> 08:31.310
with your foul mouths—

08:31.560 --> 08:33.289
you find it entertaining, huh?

08:33.390 --> 08:34.450
Who was it just now?

08:34.789 --> 08:35.320
You.

08:35.669 --> 08:36.549
And you, right?

08:36.840 --> 08:37.600
Come on, say it again.

08:37.600 --> 08:38.400
Let me hear it.

08:39.669 --> 08:40.270
What's wrong?

08:40.270 --> 08:40.669
Xiaolan...

08:40.669 --> 08:41.799
Too scared to speak?

08:41.960 --> 08:43.159
Not so brave now, huh?

08:43.270 --> 08:44.630
Xia Xiaolan!

08:45.150 --> 08:46.480
So the Xia household

08:46.480 --> 08:48.320
can't contain you anymore?

08:48.320 --> 08:49.630
Mother, she's too big for us now.

08:49.630 --> 08:50.320
Too big for us!

08:50.320 --> 08:51.360
She's out of control. So out of control.

08:51.360 --> 08:52.610
Your pathetic little household

08:52.610 --> 08:54.240
truly can't contain a great deity like me.

08:54.240 --> 08:55.120
You're all crazy.

08:55.120 --> 08:56.650
-How dare you?
-Xiaolan...

08:56.750 --> 08:58.030
Mother, she's leaving!

08:58.030 --> 08:59.440
Jingui, go after her!

08:59.950 --> 09:00.500
Xiaolan.

09:01.000 --> 09:01.630
Xiaolan!

09:04.200 --> 09:05.440
What are you doing?

09:06.000 --> 09:06.670
I'll go! I'll go!

09:06.670 --> 09:08.000
Hurry up and go after her!

09:08.000 --> 09:08.630
Xiaolan!

09:09.720 --> 09:11.150
Come back here, Xiaolan!

09:12.480 --> 09:13.030
Xiaolan!

09:13.510 --> 09:14.080
Stop right there!

09:14.080 --> 09:14.670
Xiaolan, stop running!

09:14.670 --> 09:15.200
I said stop!

09:15.200 --> 09:16.070
Come back with me, okay?

09:16.070 --> 09:16.510
Jingui.

09:16.510 --> 09:17.600
Where do you think you're going?

09:17.600 --> 09:18.930
Xiaolan, come back now!

09:19.000 --> 09:21.130
Come back with me, okay? Stop running.

09:21.390 --> 09:23.190
-Run faster, Jingui!
-Xiaolan!

09:23.670 --> 09:24.390
Xiaolan!

09:24.440 --> 09:26.120
Xia Xiaolan!

09:26.120 --> 09:27.450
Isn't that Xia Xiaolan?

09:27.600 --> 09:28.240
Xiaolan!

09:37.600 --> 09:38.790
This little troublemaker!

09:38.790 --> 09:40.080
Let's see how far you can run!

09:40.080 --> 09:40.960
Jingui,

09:41.150 --> 09:42.550
don't just pretend to help, alright?

09:42.550 --> 09:43.880
Mind your own business!

09:44.030 --> 09:45.550
I'm too old to run fast.

09:53.050 --> 09:53.910
Cheng. Cheng.

09:54.240 --> 09:56.100
Look. What's going on over there?

09:57.690 --> 10:00.350
Looks like they're bullying
those two up ahead.

10:14.840 --> 10:15.870
Wait for them to pass,

10:15.870 --> 10:17.070
and then stop the car.

10:37.200 --> 10:37.960
Jingui!

10:38.200 --> 10:39.530
-Run faster!
-Xiaolan!

10:39.720 --> 10:40.550
Stop running!

10:40.790 --> 10:42.440
What kind of driving is this? Move!

10:42.440 --> 10:43.750
Do you even know how to drive?

10:43.750 --> 10:44.840
You're blocking the way!

10:44.840 --> 10:45.510
What's going on?

10:45.510 --> 10:46.150
Get out of the way!

10:46.150 --> 10:46.870
Everyone.

10:47.240 --> 10:48.360
Excuse us. Excuse us.

10:48.360 --> 10:49.240
Our car broke down.

10:49.240 --> 10:49.910
We might need

10:49.910 --> 10:50.670
to trouble you all

10:50.670 --> 10:51.800
to help push the car.

10:52.080 --> 10:53.550
Xiaolan. Xiaolan.

10:54.390 --> 10:55.920
I really can't run anymore.

10:56.240 --> 10:57.170
Come back with me

10:57.440 --> 10:58.360
and apologize to your grandmother,

10:58.360 --> 11:00.020
then everything will be fine.

11:00.120 --> 11:00.630
Wei.

11:00.720 --> 11:01.360
Wei. Wei.

11:01.750 --> 11:03.360
Move aside! We have important business.

11:03.360 --> 11:04.550
Where are you going, aunties?

11:04.550 --> 11:05.630
Who are you calling "aunties"?

11:05.630 --> 11:06.600
Bro, come on.

11:06.670 --> 11:07.570
Have a cigarette.

11:07.570 --> 11:08.550
These are cigarettes from the city.

11:08.550 --> 11:09.120
Really good stuff.

11:09.120 --> 11:09.670
Try one.

11:09.670 --> 11:10.730
Have a try. Come on.

11:10.750 --> 11:12.390
Here, try one, come on.

11:12.600 --> 11:13.240
Xia Xiaolan!

11:13.240 --> 11:14.510
Easy, easy, easy.

11:14.510 --> 11:15.030
Liu Fen!

11:15.030 --> 11:15.960
What's going on?

11:16.070 --> 11:17.000
Calm down. Calm down.

11:17.000 --> 11:17.630
Get back here!

11:17.630 --> 11:18.240
There are groceries in the car.

11:18.240 --> 11:19.000
Do you want some?

11:19.000 --> 11:19.530
Let's go.

11:20.200 --> 11:21.840
-Let's go, Xiaolan...
-Xiaolan!

11:21.840 --> 11:22.270
Fen!

11:25.200 --> 11:25.670
Yong?

11:25.910 --> 11:26.790
Why are you here?

11:26.790 --> 11:27.720
What's going on?

11:28.360 --> 11:30.080
I came as soon as I heard about Xiaolan.

11:30.080 --> 11:30.940
What happened?

11:31.240 --> 11:32.700
How did you two end up here?

11:33.080 --> 11:34.910
Her grandmother was trying to beat her.

11:34.910 --> 11:37.030
Xia Xiaolan, you shameless girl!

11:37.030 --> 11:37.960
You loose woman!

11:38.080 --> 11:38.680
Zhang Cui!

11:39.360 --> 11:40.760
Shut your filthy mouths!

11:41.380 --> 11:43.080
You think the Liu family
has no one to stand up for them, huh?

11:43.080 --> 11:44.240
Stop yelling!
There are so many people around.

11:44.240 --> 11:44.790
I'll kill you both!

11:44.790 --> 11:45.390
I'm warning you,

11:45.390 --> 11:46.480
this is the Xia family's business!

11:46.480 --> 11:48.150
It's not your place to speak, Liu Yong!

11:48.150 --> 11:49.390
Harmony brings wealth, remember?

11:49.390 --> 11:50.910
Zhang Cui, Wang Jingui!

11:51.080 --> 11:51.510
Yong!

11:51.510 --> 11:53.310
Look, I, Liu Yong, am right here!

11:53.550 --> 11:54.980
Who do you think you're cursing at?

11:54.980 --> 11:56.150
Xiaolan is still injured.

11:56.150 --> 11:57.080
Let's leave now.

11:57.120 --> 11:57.630
Let's go.

11:57.630 --> 11:58.390
Let's go, Yong.

11:58.390 --> 11:58.920
Let's go.

11:59.320 --> 12:00.030
Sis. Sis.

12:00.840 --> 12:01.700
Come back here.

12:01.790 --> 12:02.600
Xia Xiaolan!

12:03.200 --> 12:03.870
Be good and get on the bike.

12:03.870 --> 12:04.600
Xiaolan, get on.

12:04.600 --> 12:05.120
Sit in the front.

12:05.120 --> 12:06.270
No one will dare bully you.

12:06.270 --> 12:06.730
Come on.

12:06.870 --> 12:07.270
Get on.

12:09.030 --> 12:10.360
No big deal. No big deal.

12:11.080 --> 12:11.480
Shoes!

12:11.840 --> 12:12.640
Hold on tight.

12:13.960 --> 12:15.120
Just you wait!

12:15.120 --> 12:16.230
Enough. Stop yelling.

12:16.230 --> 12:17.440
Why are you stopping me?

12:17.440 --> 12:18.170
Xia Xiaolan!

12:18.360 --> 12:19.200
Just you wait!

12:19.600 --> 12:20.390
We'll definitely bring you back!

12:20.390 --> 12:21.630
They just let those two leave like that?

12:21.630 --> 12:22.320
Yeah.

12:22.600 --> 12:23.320
I'm so mad.

12:23.550 --> 12:25.410
They can run but they cannot hide.

12:40.480 --> 12:41.610
I've transmigrated

12:42.870 --> 12:46.000
all the way back to 1983

12:47.360 --> 12:48.960
and become Xia Xiaolan,
carrying a terrible reputation

12:48.960 --> 12:50.870
and a failed suicide attempt.

12:52.750 --> 12:54.630
Everything here is strange to me.

12:55.630 --> 12:57.510
The only thing I know right now is that

12:57.510 --> 12:59.240
behind me are my uncle Liu Yong,

13:00.440 --> 13:01.790
my mother Liu Fen,

13:02.510 --> 13:05.120
and my aunt, Li Fengmei.

13:08.550 --> 13:09.150
Xiaolan.

13:09.630 --> 13:10.360
Does it hurt?

13:12.120 --> 13:12.960
I've always said

13:12.960 --> 13:15.360
there's not a decent person
in the Xia family.

13:15.360 --> 13:16.390
Where is that good-for-nothing Xia Dajun?

13:16.390 --> 13:17.050
Where is he?

13:17.270 --> 13:18.510
His daughter is in such trouble

13:18.510 --> 13:20.220
and he doesn't even dare make a peep!

13:20.220 --> 13:20.930
A grown man

13:20.960 --> 13:22.620
without an ounce of backbone.

13:22.630 --> 13:23.360
All day long, he just

13:23.360 --> 13:24.390
listens to his brothers

13:24.390 --> 13:25.200
and his mother

13:25.200 --> 13:26.150
talking nonsense.

13:26.150 --> 13:26.870
Turns out the whole family

13:26.870 --> 13:27.670
has been bullying Fen

13:27.670 --> 13:28.630
and Xiaolan all long.

13:28.630 --> 13:30.480
They'll be struck by lightning for this!

13:30.480 --> 13:31.910
Alright, enough. Stop shouting.

13:31.910 --> 13:32.770
Go make dinner.

13:33.030 --> 13:33.960
What's this?

13:34.440 --> 13:35.370
You bought this?

13:36.150 --> 13:37.410
Sweet noodles? You...

13:37.630 --> 13:39.600
Our homemade noodles are so much better.

13:39.600 --> 13:40.720
Tastier and cheaper.

13:40.720 --> 13:41.890
What a waste of money.

13:41.890 --> 13:43.600
What do you mean "a waste of money"?

13:43.600 --> 13:45.440
I bought these for the Xia family.

13:45.440 --> 13:46.840
If I had known their family was like that,

13:46.840 --> 13:48.480
I'd rather feed this to the dogs
than give it to them!

13:48.480 --> 13:49.000
Bro,

13:49.030 --> 13:50.440
so we're the dogs you feed now?

13:50.440 --> 13:51.570
Just go make dinner.

13:52.360 --> 13:53.480
Fengmei, I'll go with you.

13:53.480 --> 13:53.910
No, no.

13:54.000 --> 13:55.260
Just sit here and rest.

13:55.270 --> 13:56.400
It'll be ready soon.

13:57.750 --> 13:58.320
Son.

13:58.670 --> 14:00.270
Take Xiaolan inside to play.

14:01.550 --> 14:03.280
Xiaolan, let's go play horsey!

14:22.870 --> 14:23.630
Charge!

14:31.600 --> 14:33.000
I need to talk to you, Fen.

14:39.910 --> 14:40.750
Charge!

14:47.480 --> 14:48.150
Xiaolan.

14:48.520 --> 14:49.650
Does your head hurt?

14:49.670 --> 14:50.930
I'll blow on it for you.

14:55.750 --> 14:56.350
Come here.

14:56.870 --> 14:58.670
I want to ask you some questions.

14:59.120 --> 15:00.120
What's your name?

15:00.790 --> 15:01.320
Tao.

15:02.320 --> 15:03.080
Tao.

15:03.550 --> 15:05.750
So how old are you this year, Tao?

15:06.030 --> 15:06.670
Seven.

15:07.480 --> 15:08.320
Seven.

15:08.550 --> 15:09.950
So how old am I, little...

15:13.240 --> 15:14.700
How old am I this year, Tao?

15:15.120 --> 15:17.120
You were 17 last year,

15:17.320 --> 15:18.580
so you're 18 this year.

15:23.320 --> 15:25.910
And what does your father do?

15:25.960 --> 15:27.050
He works in the city

15:29.510 --> 15:30.440
as a bricklayer.

15:33.480 --> 15:34.360
A bricklayer...

15:34.360 --> 15:35.690
Xiaolan, have some too.

15:36.390 --> 15:37.320
I don't want any.

15:37.670 --> 15:38.270
Go play.

15:44.840 --> 15:46.000
With those people in the village

15:46.000 --> 15:47.200
and all their gossip,

15:47.960 --> 15:50.020
Xiaolan doesn't want to stay at home.

15:50.750 --> 15:52.510
It's fine for her to be away
for a few days.

15:52.510 --> 15:53.840
But what if Dajun comes back?

15:53.840 --> 15:54.650
What then?

15:54.870 --> 15:57.270
If he really wanted to come back,
wouldn't he have already?

15:57.270 --> 15:58.320
It must be his mother

15:58.320 --> 16:00.050
stopping him from coming back.

16:00.870 --> 16:02.200
She's not stopping him.

16:02.750 --> 16:03.870
She just said

16:04.240 --> 16:05.550
if Dajun comes back,

16:06.360 --> 16:07.510
they won't get

16:07.510 --> 16:09.110
the riverbank repair money.

16:09.550 --> 16:10.480
Fen.

16:12.270 --> 16:13.550
Your husband Xia Dajun—

16:13.550 --> 16:14.440
has he ever given you

16:14.440 --> 16:15.770
a penny of his earnings?

16:15.910 --> 16:16.550
All these years,

16:16.550 --> 16:17.910
haven't they all gone to his mother

16:17.910 --> 16:18.870
to support that Xia Ziyu

16:18.870 --> 16:19.870
and their family?

16:21.840 --> 16:22.720
Mother said

16:22.870 --> 16:24.910
it's not easy for our family
to have a college student.

16:24.910 --> 16:26.910
We should be thrifty at home
and spend liberally while travelling.

16:26.910 --> 16:28.790
My goodness, Fen.

16:28.790 --> 16:29.600
They've been bullying you

16:29.600 --> 16:30.440
like this,

16:30.510 --> 16:32.370
yet you're still defending them?

16:32.470 --> 16:34.510
I know your temperament.

16:34.790 --> 16:35.630
But at this point,

16:35.630 --> 16:36.510
you can't

16:36.510 --> 16:37.440
be so weak anymore.

16:37.440 --> 16:38.480
Not only are you suffering,

16:38.480 --> 16:40.140
but Xiaolan is suffering too.

16:40.150 --> 16:41.360
Your decision now

16:41.840 --> 16:42.720
affects Xiaolan's

16:42.720 --> 16:43.840
future happiness.

16:43.840 --> 16:45.790
She's already 18 years old.

16:46.240 --> 16:47.200
Is there anyone in the Xia family

16:47.200 --> 16:48.600
who stands up for you two?

16:48.670 --> 16:49.270
Is there anyone

16:49.270 --> 16:50.630
who speaks up for Xiaolan?

16:50.630 --> 16:52.690
They'd rather drive her to her death!

17:11.030 --> 17:12.510
-Come on, let's eat.
-Alright.

17:12.510 --> 17:12.970
Come on.

17:13.240 --> 17:13.770
Xiaolan.

17:14.720 --> 17:15.270
Fen,

17:15.480 --> 17:16.410
dinner's ready!

17:16.550 --> 17:17.400
Coming.

17:19.400 --> 17:20.440
What's that you've been holding all day?

17:20.440 --> 17:22.480
W-What is it?

17:22.480 --> 17:23.339
What's inside?

17:23.750 --> 17:25.750
Well, you know, Xiaolan is injured.

17:26.200 --> 17:27.880
So I thought I'd make
something nourishing for her.

17:27.880 --> 17:29.080
Steamed egg custard.

17:29.680 --> 17:30.160
Come on.

17:30.400 --> 17:31.070
Here.

17:31.400 --> 17:32.800
Eat up, Xiaolan, come on.

17:34.480 --> 17:35.270
Come on, eat up.

17:35.270 --> 17:35.920
The noodles are getting soggy.

17:35.920 --> 17:36.960
Come on, hurry up.

17:44.160 --> 17:44.760
I'm sorry,

17:45.750 --> 17:47.210
but I'm not your daughter.

17:50.880 --> 17:51.440
Xiaolan.

17:53.030 --> 17:54.290
Why aren't you eating?

18:01.110 --> 18:01.640
Let's...

18:02.880 --> 18:03.680
Let's all eat.

18:04.240 --> 18:05.110
Thank you all.

18:11.350 --> 18:12.210
Eat up. Come on.

18:12.640 --> 18:13.070
Eat up.

18:16.510 --> 18:18.270
You won't get full just eating this.

18:18.270 --> 18:18.680
Have more noodles.

18:18.680 --> 18:19.000
No.

18:19.270 --> 18:20.670
I don't want any vinegar.

18:36.830 --> 18:37.400
Xiaolan,

18:38.720 --> 18:40.450
sleep on this side later, okay?

18:42.790 --> 18:44.390
You'll be sleeping here too?

18:48.000 --> 18:48.550
Well...

18:49.510 --> 18:50.720
I can go sleep in the main room.

18:50.720 --> 18:52.320
There's not even a bed there.

18:54.740 --> 18:55.640
Just sleep here.

18:55.640 --> 18:56.640
Together is fine.

19:20.310 --> 19:21.310
It's really hard.

19:23.070 --> 19:24.000
How about I go get you

19:24.000 --> 19:24.880
another quilt?

19:25.240 --> 19:26.240
No, don't bother.

19:27.680 --> 19:28.210
Alright.

19:28.350 --> 19:29.950
I'll turn off the light then.

19:38.550 --> 19:39.680
They've gone to bed?

19:45.110 --> 19:47.310
I'm worried about Xiaolan's head injury.

19:47.310 --> 19:49.440
Could it leave her with some problems?

19:49.790 --> 19:50.880
Did you notice how she was talking
during the day?

19:50.880 --> 19:51.750
Weird, right?

19:52.070 --> 19:53.070
And she was not as close to us

19:53.070 --> 19:54.400
as she usually is.

19:55.160 --> 19:56.440
I've noticed that too.

19:57.720 --> 19:58.680
What a shame.

19:59.830 --> 20:01.240
I want the two of them

20:01.550 --> 20:03.350
to stay with us a bit longer.

20:04.270 --> 20:06.200
Since this matter hasn't been resolved,

20:06.200 --> 20:07.790
if they go back to the Xia family,

20:07.790 --> 20:09.520
they'll be bullied even worse.

20:10.200 --> 20:10.930
Is that okay?

20:13.070 --> 20:14.830
Well, she's your sister after all.

20:14.830 --> 20:16.890
If we don't take care of her, who will?

20:17.680 --> 20:19.210
Alright, let's go to sleep.

20:21.050 --> 20:22.450
Once things settle down,

20:22.750 --> 20:24.640
I'll go out and start earning money
right away.

20:24.640 --> 20:26.070
Don't push yourself too hard.

20:26.070 --> 20:26.830
I'm fine.

20:27.640 --> 20:28.960
With those two staying with us,

20:28.960 --> 20:30.890
you're the one who'll have it hard.

20:42.790 --> 20:43.350
Xiaolan.

20:43.790 --> 20:45.390
You'll live here from now on.

20:49.510 --> 20:50.850
Ask your parents to come.

20:50.850 --> 20:52.250
Ask your parents to come.

20:52.680 --> 20:53.550
I just remembered,

20:53.550 --> 20:54.880
you don't have parents.

21:00.030 --> 21:00.550
Coffee.

21:01.480 --> 21:02.070
Thanks.

21:03.270 --> 21:03.790
Thanks.

21:04.480 --> 21:05.030
Xia.

21:05.200 --> 21:06.930
Where's the coffee I asked for?

21:08.240 --> 21:09.240
You can have this one.

21:09.240 --> 21:09.920
Xia.

21:10.200 --> 21:11.480
Mr. Li needs this by ten.

21:11.480 --> 21:12.340
Take care of it.

21:12.550 --> 21:13.310
Print two copies of this

21:13.310 --> 21:14.570
and give them to Mr. Li.

21:19.510 --> 21:20.070
Xia.

21:21.070 --> 21:22.800
Finish this and you can go home.

21:25.720 --> 21:26.240
Okay.

21:27.980 --> 21:29.240
You signed this contract, didn't you?

21:29.240 --> 21:30.640
All our company's losses

21:30.830 --> 21:32.290
will be borne by you alone!

21:32.510 --> 21:34.240
If you can't pay compensation,

21:34.270 --> 21:35.530
get ready to go to jail!

21:40.680 --> 21:41.310
My phone.

22:24.000 --> 22:24.590
Smell it.

22:25.270 --> 22:26.530
Doesn't it smell good?

22:27.460 --> 22:28.060
Yes.

22:28.240 --> 22:28.920
It does.

22:29.580 --> 22:30.840
Let me apply it for you.

22:36.720 --> 22:38.270
Now you look beautiful.

23:40.380 --> 23:43.010
I woke up on the Xia family's bed.

23:44.350 --> 23:46.640
Maybe that's the portal
I transmigrated through.

23:46.640 --> 23:48.600
If I lie back down...

23:49.960 --> 23:50.830
Let's make something

23:50.830 --> 23:52.230
for Xiaolan to eat later.

23:52.400 --> 23:53.880
How about I make spicy soup?

23:53.880 --> 23:54.550
Doesn't she love

23:54.550 --> 23:55.970
the spicy soup I make for her the most?

23:55.970 --> 23:56.590
With a splash of vinegar—

23:56.590 --> 23:57.650
it's so delicious.

23:58.400 --> 24:00.000
But she said last night

24:00.160 --> 24:01.030
that she doesn't like vinegar.

24:01.030 --> 24:02.030
That's not right.

24:02.110 --> 24:03.270
Didn't Xiaolan use to

24:03.270 --> 24:04.530
love vinegar the most?

24:14.480 --> 24:15.880
Breakfast's ready!

24:15.900 --> 24:16.440
Tao.

24:16.460 --> 24:17.990
Hurry up and eat breakfast.

24:18.620 --> 24:19.380
Come here.

24:20.400 --> 24:21.790
Those little hands of yours.

24:21.790 --> 24:23.120
Look how dirty they are.

24:23.480 --> 24:25.080
Here, freshly steamed buns.

24:25.200 --> 24:26.110
Eat while they're warm.

24:26.110 --> 24:27.000
Eat while they're still warm.

24:27.000 --> 24:28.000
Smells so good.

24:28.510 --> 24:28.960
Here.

24:30.030 --> 24:30.830
Be careful, it's hot.

24:30.830 --> 24:32.070
Why don't you ever learn?

24:32.070 --> 24:33.000
Use chopsticks.

24:36.880 --> 24:38.340
Here, hold them properly.

24:40.000 --> 24:41.220
Auntie's steamed buns

24:41.220 --> 24:42.480
are better than Mom's.

24:42.770 --> 24:43.510
You ungrateful boy.

24:43.510 --> 24:45.830
Forgetting your mother
when Auntie's around, huh?

24:45.830 --> 24:47.680
Eat more if you like them.

24:47.680 --> 24:48.940
Our Tao will grow tall.

24:49.380 --> 24:51.110
Growing smart is what matters.

24:55.200 --> 24:55.730
Xiaolan.

24:55.960 --> 24:56.560
You're up.

24:56.680 --> 24:57.200
Come on.

24:57.350 --> 24:58.480
Come eat breakfast.

24:59.070 --> 24:59.640
Come on.

24:59.750 --> 25:01.480
We made your favorite spicy soup.

25:01.480 --> 25:02.480
Come on, Xiaolan.

25:03.720 --> 25:04.350
Come on.

25:04.920 --> 25:05.510
Hurry up.

25:15.400 --> 25:16.070
Xiaolan.

25:16.590 --> 25:19.550
Your hair looks pretty.

25:21.070 --> 25:21.510
Here.

25:22.160 --> 25:24.000
More chili for our Xiaolan.

25:24.550 --> 25:26.010
Xiaolan loves spicy food.

25:26.200 --> 25:27.000
Eat while it's still warm.

25:27.000 --> 25:28.270
I made this especially for you.

25:28.270 --> 25:30.070
Smell it. Doesn't it smell good?

25:36.160 --> 25:36.720
Eat decently.

25:36.720 --> 25:38.350
Could you not make so much noise?

25:38.350 --> 25:40.350
No one's fighting with you for food.

25:41.270 --> 25:42.200
Eat up, Xiaolan.

25:44.200 --> 25:44.800
It's okay.

25:45.270 --> 25:46.130
I'm not hungry.

25:46.310 --> 25:47.910
I'll just have a steamed bun.

26:38.720 --> 26:39.720
You can't think of doing anything foolish!

26:39.720 --> 26:40.270
Let go of me!

26:40.270 --> 26:40.880
Everything will pass!

26:40.880 --> 26:41.270
Let me go!

26:41.270 --> 26:42.400
You can't try to kill yourself!

26:42.400 --> 26:44.110
I wasn't thinking of anything foolish.

26:44.110 --> 26:46.040
You almost pushed me down, though.

26:46.550 --> 26:47.610
It's just I've been

26:48.270 --> 26:49.400
following you for a while...

26:49.400 --> 26:50.800
Why are you following me?

26:51.920 --> 26:54.380
I was worried
you might do something stupid.

26:55.880 --> 26:57.140
I saw ducks down there,

26:57.590 --> 26:58.920
so I was wondering
if there were any duck eggs.

26:58.920 --> 26:59.980
Stop following me.

27:06.240 --> 27:07.880
Watch your step, alright?

27:12.590 --> 27:13.320
My goodness.

27:13.680 --> 27:14.240
Xiaolan.

27:14.710 --> 27:15.770
Xiaolan! Xiaolan!

27:15.790 --> 27:17.960
If you want to do something, let me know.

27:17.960 --> 27:20.490
You... What duck eggs
were you talking about?

27:21.960 --> 27:22.920
Are they over there?

27:22.920 --> 27:24.320
Wait here. I'll go check.

27:35.200 --> 27:35.790
Xiaolan!

27:36.510 --> 27:37.770
There really are some!

27:39.560 --> 27:40.090
Xiaolan?

27:41.480 --> 27:42.110
Xiaolan!

27:44.510 --> 27:45.160
I'm sorry.

27:46.110 --> 27:47.420
You love your daughter very much,

27:47.420 --> 27:48.280
but I'm not her.

27:48.510 --> 27:49.440
I have to go back.

27:52.550 --> 27:53.790
Make way! Make way!

28:01.480 --> 28:02.200
Zhang.

28:02.440 --> 28:03.570
Isn't this Xiaolan?

28:03.590 --> 28:05.000
Are you going back to Dahe Village?

28:05.000 --> 28:06.060
Let's go together.

28:06.200 --> 28:07.200
Come on, get on.

28:09.400 --> 28:10.440
This can be exchanged for some money.

28:10.440 --> 28:10.750
Come on.

28:10.750 --> 28:11.210
Come on.

28:12.480 --> 28:13.030
Xiaolan.

28:13.480 --> 28:14.680
Why aren't you getting on?

28:14.680 --> 28:15.510
If you walk back,

28:15.510 --> 28:16.680
you won't make it before dark.

28:16.680 --> 28:17.740
Hurry up and get on.

28:18.640 --> 28:19.300
Be careful.

28:19.790 --> 28:20.400
Sit here, sit here.

28:20.400 --> 28:21.400
Come on, sit here.

28:21.880 --> 28:22.680
Sit tight.

28:23.640 --> 28:24.170
Alright.

28:24.570 --> 28:25.850
We had a great

28:25.880 --> 28:27.110
radish harvest this year.

28:27.110 --> 28:28.110
Hitting the road!

28:34.640 --> 28:36.550
You two, stop messing around.
Go play outside.

28:36.550 --> 28:37.200
So noisy.

28:37.440 --> 28:38.350
Grandma, tea.

28:39.440 --> 28:41.440
Oh my goodness!
Are you trying to scald me?

28:41.440 --> 28:42.640
Are you okay, Mother?

28:43.110 --> 28:43.640
Hongxia.

28:43.640 --> 28:45.370
Take these two outside to play.

28:45.680 --> 28:47.110
Look at you, so clumsy.

28:47.440 --> 28:48.160
Seriously.

28:58.000 --> 29:00.730
Our Ziyu is so much better.

29:01.440 --> 29:02.590
Now that Ziyu isn't home,

29:02.590 --> 29:03.480
let me tell you something.

29:03.480 --> 29:04.510
You both have to listen to me.

29:04.510 --> 29:06.000
Otherwise, I won't play with you.

29:06.000 --> 29:07.130
Behave yourselves.

29:46.620 --> 29:48.080
Since you brought me here,

29:48.230 --> 29:49.230
take me back.

30:03.160 --> 30:04.690
This should be about right.

30:09.990 --> 30:11.680
Goodbye, 1983.

30:16.880 --> 30:18.280
You two, go sleep inside.

30:18.440 --> 30:19.000
Go on.

30:21.480 --> 30:22.000
Mother.

30:22.680 --> 30:24.740
I don't want to work at the snack shop.

30:24.960 --> 30:26.000
How tiring that must be.

30:26.000 --> 30:27.460
Then what do you want to do?

30:27.590 --> 30:29.240
You're not cut out for school.

30:29.240 --> 30:30.960
Are you in a hurry to get married?

30:30.960 --> 30:31.960
That Wang boy

30:31.960 --> 30:33.090
hasn't come to see you for days.

30:33.090 --> 30:35.020
Isn't that because of Xia Xiaolan?

30:35.620 --> 30:37.950
Stop saying it's about Xia Xiaolan, okay?

30:38.030 --> 30:38.750
Don't you know

30:38.750 --> 30:39.920
what's really going on with yourself?

30:39.920 --> 30:41.960
Wasn't that just an excuse for others?

30:41.960 --> 30:42.960
With your stubborn attitude,

30:42.960 --> 30:44.360
who would dare marry you?

30:44.770 --> 30:45.640
I get mad whenever I see you.

30:45.640 --> 30:47.570
Take this. Don't just stand there.

31:18.880 --> 31:19.880
Why are you back?

31:22.110 --> 31:22.770
Who are you?

31:23.000 --> 31:23.750
Who am I?

31:24.030 --> 31:25.830
Did that fall mess up your brain?

31:27.100 --> 31:27.710
Mother!

31:28.510 --> 31:29.240
Don't shout.

31:29.240 --> 31:30.840
I came back to get something.

31:33.110 --> 31:34.370
Want to see what I have?

31:35.830 --> 31:36.510
Come on.

31:52.400 --> 31:53.440
A dress?

31:55.720 --> 31:57.320
You like my dress, don't you?

31:58.400 --> 31:59.680
Take it. Be quiet.

32:03.960 --> 32:04.640
So pretty.

32:08.270 --> 32:09.030
Mother! Grandma!

32:09.030 --> 32:10.160
Xia Xiaolan is leaving again!

32:10.160 --> 32:11.270
-Mother...
-Stop shouting.

32:11.270 --> 32:11.750
Shut up.

32:12.750 --> 32:13.920
Mother! Grandma!

32:14.270 --> 32:15.440
Xia Xiaolan is back,

32:15.590 --> 32:16.990
but she's leaving again!

32:17.030 --> 32:17.480
Mother!

32:17.480 --> 32:17.790
Stop there!

32:17.790 --> 32:18.960
Jingui, help hold Mother up!

32:18.960 --> 32:20.110
You stop right there!

32:20.110 --> 32:20.570
Mother.

32:22.920 --> 32:24.520
Xia Xiaolan, oh Xia Xiaolan.

32:24.550 --> 32:25.960
You think you can leave whenever you want

32:25.960 --> 32:27.890
and come back whenever you please?

32:27.920 --> 32:29.650
What do you think this place is,

32:30.240 --> 32:31.960
a marketplace?

32:32.830 --> 32:33.270
Yeah.

32:33.720 --> 32:34.680
Do you have a problem with that?

32:34.680 --> 32:36.590
I do have a problem!

32:36.750 --> 32:37.210
Mother.

32:38.830 --> 32:39.590
Let me make this clear

32:39.590 --> 32:40.320
to you today:

32:41.310 --> 32:44.030
if you dare step out that door today,

32:44.510 --> 32:46.400
I'll make sure you never set your foot

32:46.400 --> 32:48.160
back through it again!

32:49.640 --> 32:51.300
Try me if you don't believe it!

32:55.310 --> 32:55.750
Mother.

32:55.750 --> 32:56.960
Calm down. Calm down.

32:58.000 --> 32:59.400
What are you trying to do?

32:59.480 --> 33:00.310
What are you trying to do?

33:00.310 --> 33:01.110
Why are you holding the knife?

33:01.110 --> 33:01.830
Put it down! Put it down!

33:01.830 --> 33:02.880
What are you trying to do?

33:02.880 --> 33:04.280
Don't do anything crazy!

33:04.510 --> 33:04.970
Wait...

33:13.880 --> 33:14.640
Don't worry.

33:15.440 --> 33:16.570
I'll never come back

33:16.720 --> 33:18.380
to this darn place ever again.

33:22.590 --> 33:23.830
She's completely out of control.

33:23.830 --> 33:24.510
I'm telling you, Mother,

33:24.510 --> 33:25.770
it's all because of Liu Fen's spoiling.

33:25.770 --> 33:28.940
If you don't come back, then don't.

33:29.510 --> 33:32.030
Why did you have to ruin my vegetables?

33:32.240 --> 33:33.200
Don't just stand there!

33:33.200 --> 33:34.270
Hurry up and clean this up!

33:34.270 --> 33:35.000
My poor vegetables!

33:35.000 --> 33:37.200
My poor baby vegetables!

33:37.200 --> 33:37.920
Look at you.

33:37.920 --> 33:39.450
You couldn't even stop her.

33:47.920 --> 33:49.850
You're so greedy, little glutton.

33:50.200 --> 33:50.730
Alright.

33:52.480 --> 33:52.920
Fen.

33:53.200 --> 33:53.680
Yong.

33:55.270 --> 33:56.350
Is Xiaolan back yet?

33:56.350 --> 33:57.000
No.

33:57.000 --> 33:57.600
She's not.

33:58.920 --> 34:01.480
I've searched the whole village,
but I couldn't find her.

34:01.480 --> 34:03.550
Looks like I have to go to the Xia family
to check.

34:03.550 --> 34:04.110
I'll go with you.

34:04.110 --> 34:05.070
Don't.

34:05.720 --> 34:07.380
Just stay here and wait for me.

34:08.550 --> 34:10.670
Xiaolan, where have you been?

34:12.480 --> 34:14.590
I went to get my things
from the Xia family.

34:14.590 --> 34:15.920
I couldn't let them keep my stuff.

34:15.920 --> 34:16.630
You did the right thing.

34:16.630 --> 34:17.880
They shouldn't have any of it.

34:17.880 --> 34:18.840
Come on. I'm just glad you're back.

34:18.840 --> 34:19.300
Come on.

34:19.320 --> 34:20.510
Let's eat. Let's eat.

34:20.510 --> 34:21.840
We're glad you're back.

34:21.840 --> 34:22.570
Give it to me.

34:23.320 --> 34:24.000
Come on.

34:29.880 --> 34:31.480
I was about to go look for you,

34:31.840 --> 34:34.480
but your uncle was worried
we might miss each other.

34:34.480 --> 34:35.840
I thought since you like duck eggs,

34:35.840 --> 34:37.370
I picked a few extra for you,

34:37.590 --> 34:39.920
and I've been waiting for you
to come back.

34:44.110 --> 34:44.710
Thank you.

34:47.480 --> 34:48.190
Let's eat.

34:48.440 --> 34:48.900
Come on.

34:51.030 --> 34:52.090
Come on, let's eat.

34:52.480 --> 34:54.210
Xiaolan, you must be starving.

34:54.400 --> 34:55.960
1, 2, 3.

34:58.760 --> 34:59.960
It's so pretty.

35:00.320 --> 35:00.880
Isn't it?

35:00.960 --> 35:01.630
Yes, it is.

35:02.280 --> 35:03.320
I noticed

35:03.320 --> 35:04.230
how you couldn't take your eyes off this.

35:04.230 --> 35:04.960
Do you like it?

35:04.960 --> 35:05.550
I do.

35:05.670 --> 35:06.800
Thank you, Mom.

35:09.880 --> 35:10.410
Alright.

35:10.510 --> 35:12.280
Let's go spin around.

35:12.760 --> 35:14.230
Be careful. Don't drop it.

35:19.230 --> 35:20.360
Move a bit, will you?

35:21.190 --> 35:22.230
Move a bit!

35:24.150 --> 35:25.920
Why are you abandoning me too?

35:32.020 --> 35:33.660
If you were still here,

35:36.470 --> 35:37.230
would I not

35:37.230 --> 35:38.630
have to struggle so hard?

36:09.440 --> 36:10.370
The alarm clock!

36:10.550 --> 36:13.810
It must have been the alarm clock
that sent me through time.

36:17.280 --> 36:18.010
Alarm clock.

36:18.510 --> 36:19.910
Do we have an alarm clock?

36:20.280 --> 36:21.400
In the village, once the roosters crow,

36:21.400 --> 36:22.070
it's morning.

36:22.070 --> 36:23.470
Who needs an alarm clock?

36:26.280 --> 36:26.810
Xiaolan.

36:27.510 --> 36:28.480
If you want an alarm clock,

36:28.480 --> 36:30.340
I'll go to town and buy one for you.

36:36.340 --> 36:37.250
Look, Fen

36:37.280 --> 36:38.510
collected so many duck eggs.

36:38.510 --> 36:40.310
How can we possibly eat them all?

36:40.320 --> 36:40.840
I'm thinking

36:40.840 --> 36:41.670
maybe we should go to town

36:41.670 --> 36:42.710
and sell them.

36:44.630 --> 36:45.150
I'll go.

36:46.030 --> 36:48.070
This is China National Radio.

36:48.920 --> 36:49.850
Dear listeners,

36:50.400 --> 36:52.510
here are a few news briefs.

36:53.440 --> 36:54.960
According to Xinhua News Agency,

36:54.960 --> 36:55.760
with rural areas advancing

36:55.760 --> 36:58.360
the production responsibility system,

36:58.800 --> 37:01.480
this year's summer grain harvest
has been another bumper crop.

37:01.480 --> 37:03.510
Farmers are enthusiastically
selling their grain,

37:03.510 --> 37:05.440
market supply is becoming stable,

37:06.000 --> 37:07.670
and in many places,
communes and production teams

37:07.670 --> 37:08.550
are developing diversified operations
according to local conditions.

37:08.550 --> 37:10.110
Would you like a bowl of noodles?

37:10.110 --> 37:11.810
So this is what a county town

37:11.840 --> 37:13.240
looked like in the 1980s.

37:13.480 --> 37:15.080
It's actually quite lively.

37:15.920 --> 37:17.960
This market has abundant goods,

37:18.280 --> 37:18.880
so selling here

37:18.880 --> 37:20.190
would definitely not be competitive.

37:20.190 --> 37:20.840
I need to find

37:20.840 --> 37:22.760
a place where demand exceeds supply

37:22.760 --> 37:23.590
to sell you

37:23.590 --> 37:24.550
in exchange for an alarm clock.

37:24.550 --> 37:25.960
Chicken eggs, want some?

37:26.110 --> 37:27.110
Fresh and big chicken eggs!

37:27.110 --> 37:27.880
Come on.

37:28.230 --> 37:29.280
Come on, kid.

37:29.280 --> 37:30.340
Come and take a look.

37:30.340 --> 37:31.670
Come check the eggs out.

37:32.110 --> 37:32.570
Come on.

37:35.360 --> 37:36.800
Laid by free-range hens at home.

37:36.800 --> 37:37.670
Come check out the eggs.

37:37.670 --> 37:39.030
I'll come back for them later.

37:39.030 --> 37:39.760
Romaine lettuce.

37:39.760 --> 37:41.280
Potatoes! Potatoes!

37:41.280 --> 37:42.210
Come take a look!

37:42.360 --> 37:43.550
Come check them out!

37:43.550 --> 37:44.280
Garlic, 5 cents per catty.

37:44.280 --> 37:46.400
Come on, chicken eggs, very nutritious.

37:46.400 --> 37:47.400
Fresh big chicken eggs.

37:47.400 --> 37:48.440
Come on! Buy some!

37:48.710 --> 37:50.480
I'll take the potatoes at
5 cents per catty.

37:50.480 --> 37:52.670
Check this out, fresh wild duck eggs!

37:53.320 --> 37:54.510
Wild duck eggs, very delicious!

37:54.510 --> 37:56.670
How could wild duck eggs be
as tasty as chicken eggs?

37:56.670 --> 37:58.110
These are laid by hens

37:58.150 --> 37:58.920
raised at home.

37:58.920 --> 38:00.110
Come check them out.

38:00.480 --> 38:01.840
But my eggs are bigger!

38:02.230 --> 38:04.150
But my chicken eggs are fresher!

38:04.510 --> 38:05.770
But my eggs are bigger!

38:06.070 --> 38:07.280
Free-range chickens!

38:07.280 --> 38:09.150
Eggs laid by free-range hens!

38:09.840 --> 38:11.480
Come on, buddy. Take a look at these eggs!

38:11.480 --> 38:12.920
Come on, check out these eggs!

38:12.920 --> 38:13.360
Alright.

38:13.360 --> 38:13.880
Come on, young lady.

38:13.880 --> 38:15.740
Time for some marketing tactics.

38:16.150 --> 38:17.630
The red and green ones are the same price.

38:17.630 --> 38:18.110
Young lady.

38:18.110 --> 38:19.570
Come check out these eggs.

38:20.630 --> 38:21.230
Mister.

38:21.510 --> 38:23.400
I'm selling duck eggs over there.

38:23.440 --> 38:24.630
Could I get some green onions on credit?

38:24.630 --> 38:26.030
I'll pay you back after I sell my eggs.

38:26.030 --> 38:27.150
Sure, no problem.

38:27.510 --> 38:28.590
Thank you so much.

38:29.920 --> 38:31.510
Fresh wild duck eggs!

38:31.510 --> 38:32.360
Check it out!

38:32.400 --> 38:34.150
The more you buy, the better deal you get!

38:34.150 --> 38:36.410
Buy 21 eggs and get green onions for free!

38:36.590 --> 38:37.520
Come take a look!

38:37.630 --> 38:38.670
Fresh wild duck eggs.

38:38.670 --> 38:39.480
Really good stuff.

38:39.480 --> 38:40.440
I know these are duck eggs,

38:40.440 --> 38:41.440
but what does this mean?

38:41.440 --> 38:42.840
This is green onion.

38:43.000 --> 38:43.920
If you buy more than 20 eggs,

38:43.920 --> 38:44.880
I'll give you green onions for free.

38:44.880 --> 38:47.070
It's really delicious
stir-frying green onions with duck eggs.

38:47.070 --> 38:47.960
If you think it's too many

38:47.960 --> 38:48.670
and you can't finish them all,

38:48.670 --> 38:49.880
you can also make salted duck eggs
at home.

38:49.880 --> 38:51.590
If you buy more than 20,
it'll be 0.11 yuan each.

38:51.590 --> 38:52.400
Okay, I'll take 21 then.

38:52.400 --> 38:53.480
Sure, no problem.

38:54.710 --> 38:55.670
Look at these green onions.

38:55.670 --> 38:56.960
I'll give you a big bunch for free.

38:56.960 --> 38:58.280
Here are the green onions for you.

38:58.280 --> 38:59.480
-Alright.
-Here you are.

38:59.480 --> 39:00.320
Thank you. Thank you.

39:00.320 --> 39:01.440
Fresh wild duck eggs!

39:01.440 --> 39:03.070
The more you buy, the better deal you get!

39:03.070 --> 39:05.400
You can stir-fry them
with green onions at home.

39:05.400 --> 39:06.400
Sure, no problem.

39:07.230 --> 39:08.630
Alright, I have plenty.
Enough for everyone.

39:08.630 --> 39:09.550
One at a time, please.

39:09.550 --> 39:11.000
Okay, thank you.

39:11.000 --> 39:11.710
I'll take 2.

39:12.150 --> 39:13.550
Here, put them in your bag.

39:13.550 --> 39:14.880
Just a moment, let me get your change.

39:14.880 --> 39:16.480
Here you go.

39:18.000 --> 39:18.800
Here. Here.

39:21.110 --> 39:22.110
Finally my turn.

39:22.800 --> 39:23.190
Here.

39:23.590 --> 39:24.840
This is my last bunch of green onions,

39:24.840 --> 39:25.630
and I'll give them all to you.

39:25.630 --> 39:26.110
Thanks.

39:27.920 --> 39:28.670
All sold out?

39:28.840 --> 39:29.710
Yes, mister.

39:30.080 --> 39:31.600
Let me pay you back first.

39:31.630 --> 39:32.550
Alright, alright.

39:32.550 --> 39:33.550
Thank you so much.

39:33.630 --> 39:34.000
Don't mention it.

39:34.000 --> 39:34.510
If you hadn't

39:34.510 --> 39:35.190
let me sell on credit earlier,

39:35.190 --> 39:35.800
I wouldn't have been able

39:35.800 --> 39:37.070
to sell these eggs so quickly.

39:37.070 --> 39:38.320
I saved these 4 duck eggs for you.

39:38.320 --> 39:38.800
Please try them.

39:38.800 --> 39:39.150
Okay.

39:39.150 --> 39:39.920
Stir-fry them with the green onions.

39:39.920 --> 39:41.030
It's really delicious.

39:41.030 --> 39:41.440
Alright.

39:41.440 --> 39:41.880
Thank you.

39:41.880 --> 39:42.510
I'll definitely try it.

39:42.510 --> 39:43.590
Come back tomorrow, young lady.

39:43.590 --> 39:44.000
Sure.

39:50.230 --> 39:50.880
Miss,

39:51.480 --> 39:52.510
would you like a bowl of noodles?

39:52.510 --> 39:53.670
Check out this soup

39:53.670 --> 39:54.480
I made from big bones.

39:54.480 --> 39:55.230
It's really delicious.

39:55.230 --> 39:56.030
Boss, here.

39:57.110 --> 39:57.610
Alright.

39:57.610 --> 39:58.920
Here's the food coupon.

39:58.920 --> 39:59.450
Alright.

39:59.630 --> 40:00.430
And the money.

40:03.320 --> 40:04.070
What's wrong?

40:04.070 --> 40:05.480
Didn't bring any food coupons?

40:05.480 --> 40:06.140
No worries.

40:06.230 --> 40:07.150
Money is fine.

40:07.590 --> 40:08.790
It's 2 dimes per bowl.

40:09.070 --> 40:09.550
Okay,

40:09.710 --> 40:10.320
I'll have one bowl then.

40:10.320 --> 40:10.800
Sure.

40:10.960 --> 40:11.840
Find a place to sit,

40:11.840 --> 40:13.110
and I'll cook the noodles for you.

40:13.110 --> 40:14.280
Cooking noodles.

40:34.230 --> 40:35.800
9.22 yuan.

40:36.840 --> 40:38.970
Should be enough to buy an alarm clock.

40:44.440 --> 40:44.880
Cheng,

40:45.630 --> 40:47.630
let's buy some buns to eat on the way.

40:56.030 --> 40:57.160
Let's have noodles.

41:00.920 --> 41:01.400
Ma'am,

41:01.710 --> 41:02.840
two bowls of noodles, please.

41:02.840 --> 41:03.280
Sure.

41:03.400 --> 41:04.460
Find a place to sit.

41:08.630 --> 41:09.030
Cheng,

41:09.670 --> 41:11.800
is that the girl we ran into yesterday?

41:25.000 --> 41:25.920
Stop staring, Cheng.

41:25.920 --> 41:26.780
She's leaving.

41:29.510 --> 41:30.510
What are you looking at?

41:30.510 --> 41:32.310
Never seen a pretty girl before?

41:33.280 --> 41:34.440
Why are you pretending now?

41:34.440 --> 41:36.640
You've been sneaking glances for ages.

41:36.760 --> 41:38.230
I wasn't sneaking glances.

41:38.230 --> 41:39.430
I was looking openly.

41:42.360 --> 41:44.150
What's so interesting about me?

41:44.150 --> 41:45.150
You look special.

41:45.360 --> 41:47.820
You don't seem like
you're from around here.

41:49.440 --> 41:50.320
It's you.

41:50.960 --> 41:52.670
You drove past yesterday and kicked up
a cloud of dust on me,

41:52.670 --> 41:53.330
didn't you?

41:54.190 --> 41:54.880
Well, um...

41:54.880 --> 41:56.150
I was the one driving yesterday.

41:56.150 --> 41:56.950
Sorry, sorry.

41:58.630 --> 42:00.760
But it was fortunate that we happened to
pass by

42:00.760 --> 42:01.800
and helped you out of that situation.

42:01.800 --> 42:04.460
I guess that evens things out between us,
right?

42:04.710 --> 42:05.840
Can I get to know you?

42:07.280 --> 42:08.480
Since we're even now,

42:08.510 --> 42:10.480
there's really no need for that, right?

42:10.480 --> 42:11.150
Ma'am,

42:11.630 --> 42:13.360
is there a watch shop nearby?

42:13.630 --> 42:14.430
Yes, there is.

42:14.480 --> 42:16.340
Just go straight down this street

42:16.400 --> 42:18.550
and through Anping Alley,
and you'll find it.

42:18.550 --> 42:19.480
Okay, thank you.

42:19.840 --> 42:20.770
You're welcome.

42:21.110 --> 42:23.310
Excuse me, could you please move aside?

42:33.710 --> 42:34.280
Cheng,

42:36.070 --> 42:37.710
not a good start, huh?

43:03.280 --> 43:04.010
Xia Xiaolan.

43:04.670 --> 43:06.000
Sold all your duck eggs?

43:06.630 --> 43:07.890
Didn't save any for us?

43:10.400 --> 43:12.000
You bitch! How dare you kick me!

43:12.000 --> 43:12.550
Let me go!

43:12.590 --> 43:12.960
Get over here!

43:12.960 --> 43:14.550
You think we don't know
what you're really like?

43:14.550 --> 43:15.150
Let me go!

43:15.510 --> 43:16.000
Help!

43:16.000 --> 43:16.670
Didn't you have a great time

43:16.670 --> 43:17.670
with Zhang Erlai?

43:17.760 --> 43:19.670
-Let me go!
-Why pretend to be chaste now?
